We are building India’s first soft baked cookie brand & here’s what we’ve learnt so far!

1. Product is just the beginning
2. Nothing is perfect on Day 1
3. It takes years to become an ‘overnight success’
4. One man armies don’t win wars
5. It’s important to have fun!
